<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrīḥ</hi>— Aḷanāṭṭu pullinallūruṭai
<lb n="2" break="no"/>yār kaṇṇuṭai Īccuramuṭaiya nāyaṉā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṟku <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>vikkiramapāṇṭiyatevaṟku yāṇṭu <hi rend="grantha">5</hi>
<lb n="4" break="no"/>vatiṉ ṉetir 2<g type="dash"/>vatu mutal teṉkallaka nāṭ
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṭu Uṭaiyār mūlattāṉamuṭaiya nāyaṉā 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>r tirumaṭaiviḷākattil Eṭuttapātam pakava
<lb n="7" break="no"/>tiyāḻvāṉāṉa poṉmāḷikaik kālakate<note n="325-1">Stops here.</note>
</p>

